a U.S. marshal named John Carruthers (John Wayne) witnesses a robbery, but the town's sheriff Jake suspects him of being the culprit. At the same time, the most prominent citizen of the town is plotting to rob everyone in the area.

B&W version https://youtu.be/2LiVnDZbO-E

Stars: John Wayne, Eleanor Hunt, George 'Gabby' Hayes
Genre: Colorized classic, Western
